Package: rangeos-system
Version: 0.2.31
Architecture: all
Maintainer: RangeOS AI Project <ops@rangeos.ai>
Depends: systemd (>= 245), rangeos-core
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: RangeOS AI System Integration Layer
 Installs systemd unit files, session wrapper, preflight validator,
 and the health provider daemon.
 Provides system-level and user-level service orchestration for the
 full RangeOS AI microservice mesh via rangeos-core.target.
